headline: BofA Names Kelly Firment President of Delaware
summary: Bank of America has named Kelly Firment, Small Business and Vehicle Client Servicing executive, president of Bank of America Delaware. She succeeds Chip Rossi, who led the market for more than 15 years and retired this past June after a 40-year career with Bank of America.

headline: Siemens Energy AG stock added to BofA Europe 1 list of top ideas
summary: Investing.com -- Bank of America analysts reiterated their Buy rating on Siemens Energy AG, raising the price target to €150 from €110 and adding the stock to the firm’s Europe 1 list of top ideas in a note Thursday.
